videos.description: Kentucky swings the ball around and gets it to Malik Monk for the long jumper.
videos.headline: Good Kentucky ball movement leads to a Monk basket

videos.description: Malik Monk gets the ball, drives in and hits the long off-balanced jumper, while also drawing the foul.
videos.headline: Monk hits long off-balanced jumper, draws the foul

videos.description: De'Aaron Fox misses a jumper, Edrice Adebayo is there to slam the dunk on the putback.
videos.headline: Adebayo slams down putback dunk

videos.description: Tennessee in transition, Jordan Bowden gives to Robert Hubbs III, who one-hand slams it in to increase Tennessee's lead over Kentucky.
videos.headline: Hubbs III slams it in transition for Vols

videos.description: Kentucky head coach John Calipari explains what his team needs to do better in the second half against Tennessee.
videos.headline: Calipari: 'We just gotta do a better job'

videos.description: Lew Evans splits the Kentucky defense, lays it in and draws a foul to extend the Tennessee lead.
videos.headline: Evans splits D for nice lay-in and foul

videos.description: Grant Williams picks off  Kentucky pass.  Volunteers running the other way, Jordan Bowden gets the ball and sinks the layup.
videos.headline: Defense turns into offense for Tennessee

videos.description: Off a De'Aaron Fox turnover, Robert Hubbs III powers in a two-handed slam for Tennessee.
videos.headline: Kentucky turnover leads to Tennessee dunk in win

videos.description: Tennessee coach Rick Barnes and Robert Hubbs III break down what Tennessee did right in order to knock off Kentucky.
videos.headline: Barnes happy for team after win over Kentucky
